le=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615514\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615514\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 20, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qug1665702641707.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qug1665702641707.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qug1665702641707.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qug1665702641707\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Strip Image</span> widget property specifies an image that can be used as a background for the complete horizontal tab strip.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qug1665702641707__p_d107810e1_d107811e1_d107812e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>TabStripImage<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">@<var class=\"keyword varname\">ImageFile</var></code>\n      or <code class=\"ph codeph\">^<var class=\"keyword varname\">GlyphName</var></code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qug1665702641707__section_am3_jzd_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d921843e71\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"qug1665702641707__table_d12704e1_d12705e1_d12706e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Applicable only for single line, horizontal tab\n                strips, and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Default Image</span> must be defined. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qug1665702641707__section_lh3_lzd_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d921843e120\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qug1665702641707__p_d107819e1_d107820e1_d107821e1\">When an image is defined for <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Strip\n          Image</span>, it is automatically expanded to fit the complete width of the tab\n        widget.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qug1665702641707__p_d107822e1_d107823e1_d107824e1\">You can set the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Strip Image</span>\n        property to ensure a consistent background for the whole strip when Default Image is a\n        transparent image, or when tabs are transparent images and the selected one has a color.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qug1665702641707__section_arg_mzd_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d921843e138\">Using in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qug1665702641707__p_d107828e1_d107829e1_d107830e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span> or\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span> to set or get the property and its value. For more\n        information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zie1665702558978.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zie1665702558978.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of a field.\">$properties</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aud1705998763272.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1705998763272.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field.\">$fieldproperties</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"qug1665702641707__pre_c5x_nzd_1xb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD) = \"TabStripImage=@bluegradient.png\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qug1665702641707__section_t5c_4zd_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d921843e170\">Example: Effect of Tab Strip Image</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qug1665702641707__p_d107834e1_d107835e1_d107836e1\">If no image is defined for <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Strip\n          Image</span>, the background of the tab strip (in the red block) follows the Windows\n        theme:</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"qug1665702641707__fig_d107837e1_d107838e1_d107839e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>No Tab Strip Image</figcaption>\n<br/><img alt=\"No Tab Strip image\" class=\"image\" id=\"qug1665702641707__image_qw5_112_1xb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/tabstripimage_no.png?_LANG=enus\"/><br/>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qug1665702641707__p_d107843e1_d107844e1_d107845e1\">In the following illustration, the same image is\n        defined for both the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Default Image</span> and the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Strip\n          Image</span>.</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"qug1665702641707__fig_d107846e1_d107847e1_d107848e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 2. </span>Tab Strip Image Defined</figcaption>\n<br/><img alt=\"Tab Strip Image Defined\" class=\"image\" id=\"qug1665702641707__image_l1j_tzd_1xb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/tabstripimage.png?_LANG=enus\"/><br/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qug1665702641707__section_egt_c12_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d921843e216\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gyf1688451219719.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gyf1688451219719.html\" title=\"The utabex widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. The utabex widget is highly customizable, allowing extensive control over the appearance and behavior of the tabs. Uniface provides a logical widget called TabEx, which is mapped to utabex.\">utabex (TabEx)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dte1665702632952.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Default Image (ImgDefault)</a><p>The image that is displayed as the button or tab.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615514\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615514\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Tab Strip Image (TabStripImage) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 20, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The Tab Strip Image widget property specifies an image that can be used as a background for the complete horizontal tab strip. \" TabStripImage = @ ImageFile or ^ GlyphName \" Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: Applicable only for single line, horizontal tab strips, and Default Image must be defined. Description When an image is defined for Tab Strip Image , it is automatically expanded to fit the complete width of the tab widget. You can set the Tab Strip Image property to ensure a consistent background for the whole strip when Default Image is a transparent image, or when tabs are transparent images and the selected one has a color. Using in ProcScript You can use $properties or $fieldproperties to set or get the property and its value. For more information, see $properties and $fieldproperties . $fieldproperties(FLD) = \"TabStripImage=@bluegradient.png\" Copy Example: Effect of Tab Strip Image If no image is defined for Tab Strip Image , the background of the tab strip (in the red block) follows the Windows theme: Figure 1. No Tab Strip Image In the following illustration, the same image is defined for both the Default Image and the Tab Strip Image . Figure 2. Tab Strip Image Defined Applies To utabex (TabEx) Related Links Default Image (ImgDefault) The image that is displayed as the button or tab. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}